comment: A third case of the Wuhan coronavirus has been confirmed in the United States, authorities said.The individual traveled from Wuhan to Orange County, California. He is now being held in isolation in a local hospital and is in good condition. | via @cnni
The other two confirmed cases in the US that have been identified are in Washington state and Illinois | via @cnni
